question: A page is not functioning or loading on the proxy
answer: Our web servers are either under really high load, or the web page you tried accessing is not currently supported.

question: How so I get back to the main page after opening the proxy
answer: If you hover your mouse on the top of the page, a menu will appear with options to close, reload and copy a URL to the proxied page

question: Is my information secure
answer: Incognito, in its unmodified state from its GitHub repo, does not collect your data. However, users can host their own instance of this website that could have been modified to collect user data

question: Why is GeForce Now is responding with "403 Access Denied"
answer: At the moment, too many people are using GeForce Now on our servers. Try again later.
